data.description: LOCATION! EASY ACCESS 3/2/2 concrete block home w/scr'd porch & private fenced backyard on quiet street. The solar panels offer low electric bills$ The white kitchen includes all appliances, soft-close cabinets, pantry & Granite countertops. The eat in kitchen has bay window w/built-in seating. Split floor plan w/Cathedral ceil & tile. Bedrooms 2 & 3 have decorative chair rail & laminate. Bath 2 has decorative mirror, Granite & glass shower door. Master suite with hardwood bamboo, walkin closet, large tub/shower & linen closet. New water heater. Private fenced backyard offers concrete patio & storage shed. Plenty of room for a pool. The right side of the home offers gravel area for boat/RV parking. Walk to work, shopping & restaurants. Minutes to Tradition I-95 & Turnpike for commuters.
